title: Eetwinkel 't Hof Welgelegen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Western, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Health food shop and cafe offering fresh local fruit and veggies as well as dry goods such as spreads, soy yogurt, chocolates and more. Small seating area. The changing menu includes mostly vegetarian baguettes, toasties, salads. Vegan options upon request.
